---
title: Caribbean Veggie Mince Chilli with Coconut Rice & Charred Corn Salad
description: We’ve packed the signature flavours of the Caribbean into this mouth-watering veggie mince chilli, served with fluffy coconut rice and a
refreshing corn salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-beef-chilli-coconut-rice-a04e3a2c.jpg
